  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Commitment by CDC to the Growth Catalyst Partners investment fund. The core focus of the fund is on financial inclusion. Lack of access to finance is a major barrier to India&apos;s economic growth. Delhi-based Growth Catalyst Partners aims to make finance available to underserved and underbanked communities for a range of uses. These include finance and working capital to enable India&apos;s small and medium sized businesses, including rural smallholders and agribusinesses, to modernise and expand. Our investment will also provide access to affordable housing finance and affordable healthcare. This will have a direct impact on reducing poverty.</narrative>
  </description>
